      <title>据称克里姆林宫双重间谍在选举前扰乱奥地利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/alleged-kremlin-double-agent-roils-austria-ahead-of-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名涉嫌用秘密交易换取克里姆林宫现金的高级反情报官员被捕，正在全国选举前颠覆奥地利政治，并巩固该国作为间谍天堂的声誉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/alleged-kremlin-double-agent-roils-austria-ahead-of-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 09:32:06 GMT</pubDate>
